tournament.name: Sri Lanka Schools Debating Championship 2023
tournament.motion: THR the rising popularity of exotic expeditions for the ultra rich (ex: Oceangate’s Titan, Virgin Galactic, dearMooon expedition by SpaceX)OceanGate’s Titan refers to a Submersible vessel operated by OceanGate Expeditions which takes persons to explore the Titanic Wreckage. Recently the Titan vessel carrying five wealthy persons was lost in the voyage. Virgin Galactic is an American spaceflight company that focuses on space tourism, the enterprise of sending humans for space travel for recreational purposes. The dearMoon project is a lunar tourism mission which aims to carry eight accomplished artists on a voyage around the moon. The project is financed by Japanese billionaire Yusaku Maezawa and will use a SpaceX vessel for the journey.
THR the Sri Lankan meme culture
